#import libraries and install packages
library(openair)
library(lubridate)
#Import data
ad_summer2012 <- read.csv2("https://raw.githubusercontent.com/lourdesvera/Community_Air_Montoring/master/Wind_Analyses/Armourdale_10yrs.csv", header = TRUE, sep = ",", stringsAsFactors = FALSE )
armourdale
#rename columns
colnames(ad_summer2012) = c("Year", "Month", "Day", "Temperature", "ws", "wd")
#change some column formats
ad_summer2012$Temperature <- as.numeric(ad$Temperature)
ad_summer2012$ws <- as.numeric(ad$ws)
ad_summer2012$wd <- as.numeric(ad$wd)
#Concatenate day, month, year and convert that column into date/time format
ad_summer2012$date <- make_date(year = ad_summer2012$Year, month = ad_summer2012$Month , day = ad_summer2012$Day)
